thread.title: Chemical weapons in Syria: A history of obstruction

title: Chemical weapons in Syria: A history of obstruction
text:
Chemical weapons in Syria: A history of obstruction   01:59 
Chemical weapons inspectors hoping to reach the suspected gas attack site in Syria that sparked the West's retaliatory strikes were delayed on Monday. Similar efforts over the years faced systematic obstruction.
